lilo-installer (0.0.13) unstable; urgency=low

  * Make it possible to build this package using binary-arch target.
    (Closes: 184287)
  * Correct call do db_input, it should only ignore return value 30
    meaning the question was not displayed.  All other return values
    are errors.
  * Add myself as uploader for this package.
  * Make sure to use the same default console as the linux kernel, and
    let the user know when a serial console is enabled.  Based on patch
    from Joe Nahmias.  (Closes: #191588)
  * AndrÃ© LuÃ­s Lopes
